listitem.para:
The following command runs the tests for self permissions and sets up the database

  for a user with subjectDN user2SubjectDN:

        casadmin$ ant -f share/globus_cas_unit_test/cas-test-build.xml user1TestService

To test as the second user, generate a proxy for the subject DN specified

      for the second user:

        casadmin$ java org.globus.tools.ProxyInit
